_sText:
The bomb-site is at the bottom.
There is a long drop at the bottom so beware!
This is a modified version of de_tchs_mixer or de_mixer. This version has smaller panes of glass that are easier to damage, and a higher wall at the top to prevent so many grenades from landing on your face!
Darker lighting with red lighting in the bomb area.
v3.0 - initial release
v3.1 - added big drop at bottom
v3.2 - added bombsite decal
v3.3 - scrapped
v3.4 - complete redesign, back to 10 floor original, better lighting, cubemaps working, performance enhancements, bugfixes, no bombsite decal
v3.5 - fixed bomb from falling down the pit of doom
v3.6 - the bomb still seems to fall through when travelling at high speed - got rid of the pit of doom and added a tunnel of doom instead
v3.7 - introduction of a new void underneath a reworked lower deck
v3.8 - performance improvements, cubemaps (sorry this increases the filesize by 4MB) apparently working
